
I gasped, standing up quickly. "Are you one of Goddess Palutena's Angels?!"
He nodded his head, seeming excited as well."Yes I am!"
"And you liked my singing..?" I asked slowly walking over to him.
Once again he nodded his head, his hair bouncing as he did so. "Yup, I did. It was really pretty." He gave me a small, cute smile.
"Thanks. " a small blush formed on my face, and I smiled back shyly.
"Oh,hey I'm Pit by the way!"He stopped leaning on the tree and walked over to me.